<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>MFA Verification Code</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px;">
    <h1 style="color: #2c3e50; margin-top: 0;">MFA Verification Code</h1>
    
    <p>Hello,</p>
    
    <p>You requested a Multi-Factor Authentication verification code. Use the code below to complete your login:</p>
    
    <div style="background-color: #fff; border: 2px solid #3498db; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h2 style="color: #3498db; font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: 5px; margin: 0;">{{otp}}</h2>
    </div>
    
    <p style="color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 14px;">This code will expire in <strong>{{expiresIn}}</strong>.</p>
    
    <p style="color: #e74c3c; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;">If you didn't request this code, please ignore this email or contact support if you have concerns.</p>
    
    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; margin: 20px 0;">
    
    <p style="color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 12px; margin: 0;">This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>


